								"html": "<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t\tThe Salvation Army Center of Hope Family Shelter is the only family emergency shelter in Forsyth County. It provides a safe refuge and the resources to give families and individuals a fresh start and a return to permanent housing and stability. The Center of Hope gives shelter to single mothers, single fathers, and parents with children.&nbsp;\n\t</p>",
